  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether BVS(Bioresorbable Vascular Scaffold)
      implantation with optimal medical therapy can improve the outcome of patients with variant
      angina and moderate coronary artery disease.
    </textblock>
